author: Jason Lemon
title: Florida Is the Only U.S. State With Over 5,000 Coronavirus Cases That Hasn't Issued A Statewide Stay At Home Order
description: "The task force has not recommended that to me," Governor Ron DeSantis said.
content:
Florida is now the only state with more than 5,000 confirmed cases of coronavirus that has not issued a statewide lockdown.
